    "content": "Song: Shout\r\nArtist: Tears for Fears\r\n\r\n\r\nr = rest\r\n\r\n  Shout, shout...  These are the... Come on...   \r\n\r\n[tab]   G               Eb                C           G\r\nG:-------------------------------------------------------------\r\nD:-----------------1-------------------------------------------\r\nA:-----------------------------------3-------------------------\r\nE:-3---------------------------------------------3-------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse: \r\n\r\n  In modern times...\r\n\r\n[tab]  Bb                 C\r\nG:-------------------------------|\r\nD:-------------------------------| -repeat 3 more times-\r\nA:-1-1--1-1-1--------3-3--3-3-3--|\r\nE:-------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nChorus:\r\n \r\n   Shout, shout...\r\n\r\n[tab]   G                 Eb                C                \r\nG:-------------------------------------------------------------\r\nD:-------------------1111111r-1111111r-------------------------\r\nA:-------------------------------------3333333r-3333333r-------\r\nE:-3333333r-3333333r-------------------------------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]   G \r\nG:-------------------------|\r\nD:-------------------------|\r\nA:-------------------------|\r\nE:-33333333r--33333333r----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n-repeat verse-\r\n\r\n-repeat chorus 2 times-\r\n\r\n\r\nBreakdown\r\n\r\n   C               G\r\n\r\n[tab]G:--0--------------0-------------------------------------------\r\nD:-------------------------------------------------------------\r\nA:--3----------------------------------------------------------\r\nE:-----------------3-------------------------------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\nBass solo:\r\n\r\n[tab]   G\r\nG:-------------------------------------------------------------\r\nD:-5-r----3---5------------3-5---3---3-5-----------------------\r\nA:------5---5----------3-5---------5---------------------------\r\nE:-------------3-----3---------3---------3---------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]   G \r\nG:-------------------------------------------------------------\r\nD:-5-r----3---5------------3---5-------------------------------\r\nA:------5---5------------5---5---5-----------------------------\r\nE:-------------r---333-------------3---3-----------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n-repeat verse and chorus as needed-\r\n\r\n\r\nTranscribed by Christopher Funicelli\r\nComments or suggestions, please email me at cfunz@aol.com",
